HEADWORD: Olay
<hw>O"lay</hw> <pr>(⟦omac⟧"l⟦imac⟧)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[Tamil <ets>⟦omac⟧lai</ets>.]</ety> <def>Palm leaves, prepared for
being written upon with a style pointed with steel.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>ola</asp>.]</altsp> <rj><au>Balfour (Cyc. of
India).</au></rj>⟦br⟧
